'''Pico-12 Squad''' were a squad of five veteran members of the [[Republican Army]] who were present at the [[Battle of Mandalore (pre-Naboo)|Battle of Mandalore]]. It is unknown if this squad survived for the final victory or not.<ref name="BFM">{{ChallengeCite|58|Battle for Mandalore}}</ref>

